name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dialer for use with InteliCall systems

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Overrides the default behavior of 'tel:' links, causing your InteliCall phone to dial. *Not developed or designed by InteliCall

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Uses the InteliCall Api to dial the number on screen, converting traditional tel: links to a call to InteliCall which triggers your phone to dial.
